  <brief_title>The Application of the ELFI-TECH Monitor for Perioperative Hemodynamic Measurements</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Application of the ELFI-TECH Monitor for Measurement of Blood Pressure, Cardiac Output and Extend of Regional and Neuraxial Anesthesia: The Elfitor Study</official_title>
